room_title: Escape room "Lab of the Lost" by The Quandary Escape Rooms in Chicago
room_address: 3205 N Clark St Suite 100, Chicago, IL 60657
room_description: You are a team of scientists and other professionals in inSyn Genetics Lab.  The lab is located in a remote jungle, away from prying eyes.  They have been conducting some experiments on prehistoric DNA and have managed to bring dinosaurs back from extinction!  However, on your trip, communications suddenly go down. You must figure out what is happening before things get disasterous.
